{"tid":1172576,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"川普傷了華為 三星成大贏家","createTime":"2019-05-26T13:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T16:35:14.000Z","uid":85180,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"53ce1f64190f04314b88a11f6d6df0fdefc13521","tid":1172576,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"川普傷了華為 三星成大贏家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/201905251335400461_AG097.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F201905251335400461_AG097.jpg&h=0a9d6615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國封殺華為，將使韓國三星得利。圖為華為在泰國曼谷的經銷商。(路透)<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/201905251335400502_AG097.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F201905251335400502_AG097.jpg&h=fa6e06ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國封殺華為，將使韓國三星得利。圖為三星在南韓首爾的辦公大樓。(路透)<br />\n業界分析家指出，華為競爭對手三星（Samsung），可能是華為風波的大贏家，因為沒有安卓作業系統的華為手機，很難在中國以外的市場和三星手機競爭。<br />\n<br />\n分析家說，三星的摺疊式手機出航不順，本來「全球第一手機王」地位開始動搖，川普臨門一腳整華為，使得三星得以穩固地位，美國的蘋果公司成為唯一可能威脅三星的手機廠商。<br />\n<br />\n華為即使明年順利推出比三星Galaxy Fold更好的摺疊式手機，但自稱「獨家研發」的鴻蒙作業系統如果不能提供谷歌電郵及地圖等服務的話，對消費者的吸引力將大為降低。<br />\n<br />\n這對本來被華為追的很辛苦的三星是好消息。根據國際資料公司(International Data Corp.)的統計，今年首季三星全球智慧型手機的市占率比一年前下降了8.1%，降為23.1%；華為則猛增50％，到19%。<br />\n<br />\n第三名的蘋果市占率僅11.7%；小米排名第四，市占率8%；即使華為市場繼續縮小，蘋果和小米仍很難追上三星。<br />\n<br />\nUBS專家群認為，川普傷了華為，對蘋果在中國的市場不利。媒體已經報導，川普下令美國企業「斷供」華為後，不少中國人民主動呼籲抵制蘋果。<br />\n<br />\n中國是蘋果的第三大市場，2018年末季在中國市占率達12％，若遭杯葛的話，要追上三星更難了。<br />\n<br />\n華為在三星推出評價不太好的Galaxy Fold不到幾天，就發表自己的摺疊式手機Mate X，但還沒有確定什麼時候上市，因為不確定能否繼續使用谷歌安卓系統，美國政府給它三個月的寬限，到8月19日。能否在那之前就上市，目前仍在未定之天。<br />\n<br />\n小米和摩托羅拉也在做摺疊式手機，但投入的力度顯然不如三星和華為，因此，三星修正Galaxy Fold缺點再出發的話，很可能霸占摺疊市場一段時間。"},{"pid":"1dcc134d3dd9c7843a4a4bc1cf9de38bfc218845","tid":1172576,"uid":85180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T13:57:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三星成大贏家</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f395025a219117ea66cc7457e448ebd76fc476a8","tid":1172576,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1dcc134d3dd9c7843a4a4bc1cf9de38bfc218845","tid":1172576,"uid":85180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T13:57:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三星成大贏家</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T14:04:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大韓民國成最大贏家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/09/Flag_of_South_Korea.svg/2000px-Flag_of_South_Korea.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F0%2F09%2FFlag_of_South_Korea.svg%2F2000px-Flag_of_South_Korea.svg.png&h=24eb7397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.moedict.tw/大韓民國.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moedict.tw%2F%E5%A4%A7%E9%9F%93%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B.png&h=6e0e7632&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b397d3e90cc465db02636b0170adbcb40d27e74","tid":1172576,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"不少中國人民主動呼籲抵制蘋果。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126d8a84b7d3f8c562c1e3f33ce73f7c6f987c9b","tid":1172576,"uid":85180,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"f395025a219117ea66cc7457e448ebd76fc476a8","tid":1172576,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1dcc134d3dd9c7843a4a4bc1cf9de38bfc218845","tid":1172576,"uid":85180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T13:57:40.000Z","ms